data.description: This 2 story home with hill country flair is located in the highly sought-after community of Creekside Ranch. This property features an open concept floor plan with 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and a powder room.  The second story features a game room with plenty of room for family game nights.  The property features granite and quartz countertops throughout, high ceilings, neutral colors and a hill country flair.  The large backyard boasts a stunning custom Texas shaped pool with a covered patio perfect for entertaining and backyard bbq. Creekside Ranch has a clubhouse, park, and splash pad for all residents.
